{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/Mongo-DB-2","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"0489868f-42b1-52ba-b84c-99173ee8ff33","html":"<h1 id=\"mongodb의-database-collection-document-생성제거\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#mongodb%EC%9D%98-database-collection-document-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1%EC%A0%9C%EA%B1%B0\" aria-label=\"mongodb의 database collection document 생성제거 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>mongoDB의 Database, Collection, Document 생성,제거</h1>\n<h2 id=\"database의-생성--제거\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#database%EC%9D%98-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1--%EC%A0%9C%EA%B1%B0\" aria-label=\"database의 생성  제거 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Database의 생성 / 제거</h2>\n<h3 id=\"database의-생성-use-database_name-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#database%EC%9D%98-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1-use-database_name-\" aria-label=\"database의 생성 use database_name  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Database의 생성( use Database_name )</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">use DATABASE_NAME</code>을 사용하면 database가 존재하지 않는다면 새로 생성하게 된다.\n만약 존재한다면 해당 database내부로 진입하게 된다.</p>\n<p>새로운 db 생성 혹은 해당 db 접속</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token operator\">></span> use <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">test</span>\nswitched to db <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">test</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>현재 사용중인 데이터베이스 확인</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token operator\">></span> db\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">test</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>db 전체 조회 아래는 현재 내 mongoDB의 db조회 상황이다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token operator\">></span> show dbs\nadmin   <span class=\"token number\">0</span>.000GB\nconfig  <span class=\"token number\">0</span>.000GB\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">local</span>   <span class=\"token number\">0</span>.000GB\nprac    <span class=\"token number\">0</span>.002GB\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> show databases\nadmin   <span class=\"token number\">0</span>.000GB\nconfig  <span class=\"token number\">0</span>.000GB\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">local</span>   <span class=\"token number\">0</span>.000GB\nprac    <span class=\"token number\">0</span>.002GB</code></pre></div>\n<p>현재 <code class=\"language-text\">test</code>db에 접속해 있지만 전체목록에서는 보이지 않는다. 그 이유는 Document를 하나라도 추가해야하기 때문이다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token operator\">></span> db.test.insert<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string\">\"name\"</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"아뇽하세용\"</span>, <span class=\"token string\">\"age\"</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"999\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nWriteResult<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"nInserted\"</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> show dbs\nadmin   <span class=\"token number\">0</span>.000GB\nconfig  <span class=\"token number\">0</span>.000GB\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">local</span>   <span class=\"token number\">0</span>.000GB\nprac    <span class=\"token number\">0</span>.002GB\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">test</span>    <span class=\"token number\">0</span>.000GB</code></pre></div>\n<p>test가 새로 생겼다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"database의-제거-dbdropdatabase-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#database%EC%9D%98-%EC%A0%9C%EA%B1%B0-dbdropdatabase-\" aria-label=\"database의 제거 dbdropdatabase  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Database의 제거( db.dropDatabase() )</h3>\n<p>database를 제거하려면 삭제하려는 db에 접속해주어야합니다. <code class=\"language-text\">use</code>로 switch 시켜주어야합니다.</p>\n<p>삭제하려는 db에 들어왔다면 <code class=\"language-text\">db.dropDatabase()</code>를 사용합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token operator\">></span> use <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">test</span>\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> db.dropDatabase<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"dropped\"</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"test\"</span>, <span class=\"token string\">\"ok\"</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"collection-생성--제거\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#collection-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1--%EC%A0%9C%EA%B1%B0\" aria-label=\"collection 생성  제거 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Collection 생성 / 제거</h2>\n<h3 id=\"collection-생성--dbcreatecollection-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#collection-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1--dbcreatecollection-\" aria-label=\"collection 생성  dbcreatecollection  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Collection 생성 ( db.createCollection() )</h3>\n<p>Collection을 생성할때는 db.createCollection(name,[option]) 명령어를 사용한다.</p>\n<p>name에는 생성하려는 컬렉션 이름을 나타낸다.</p>\n<p>option은 document 타입으로 구성된 해당 컬렉션의 설정값으로 선택적인 매개변수이므로 생략해도되며 필요에 따라 사용하면된다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"option\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#option\" aria-label=\"option permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Option</h4>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">Field</th>\n<th align=\"center\">Type</th>\n<th align=\"center\">설명</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">capped</td>\n<td align=\"center\">Boolean</td>\n<td align=\"center\">이 값을 true 로 설정하면 capped collection 을 활성화 시킵니다. Capped collection 이란, 고정된 크기(fixed size) 를 가진 컬렉션으로서, size 가 초과되면 가장 오래된 데이터를 덮어씁니다. 이 값을 true로 설정하면 size 값을 꼭 설정해야합니다.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">autoIndex</td>\n<td align=\"center\">Boolean</td>\n<td align=\"center\">이 값을 true로 설정하면, _id 필드에 index를 자동으로 생성합니다. 기본값은 false 입니다.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">size</td>\n<td align=\"center\">number</td>\n<td align=\"center\">Capped collection 을 위해 해당 컬렉션의 최대 사이즈(maximum size)를 ~ bytes로 지정합니다.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">max</td>\n<td align=\"center\">number</td>\n<td align=\"center\">해당 컬렉션에 추가 할 수 있는 최대 갯수를 설정합니다.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>collection 만들고 조회해보기</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token operator\">></span> db.createCollection<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'호박고구마'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"ok\"</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> show collections\n호박고구마</code></pre></div>\n<p>option 넣을시</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">db.createCollection<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"호박고구마\"</span>, <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">..</span>. capped: true,\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">..</span>. autoIndex: true,\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">..</span>. size: <span class=\"token number\">123456</span>,\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">..</span>. max: <span class=\"token number\">10000</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">..</span>. <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>그리고 document를 추가하면서 자동으로 생성시킬 수도 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token operator\">></span> db.메타톤.insert<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">\"간장게장\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nWriteResult<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"nInserted\"</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> show collections\n메타톤\n호박고구마</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"coleection-제거-dbcollection_namedrop\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#coleection-%EC%A0%9C%EA%B1%B0-dbcollection_namedrop\" aria-label=\"coleection 제거 dbcollection_namedrop permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Coleection 제거 (db.COLLECTION_NAME.drop())</h3>\n<p>제거할 때는 database때와 같이 <code class=\"language-text\">drop()</code>을 사용하면된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token operator\">></span> show collections\n메타톤\n호박고구마\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> \n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> db.메타톤.drop<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token boolean\">true</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"document-생성--제거\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#document-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1--%EC%A0%9C%EA%B1%B0\" aria-label=\"document 생성  제거 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Document 생성 / 제거</h2>\n<h3 id=\"document-생성-dbcollection_nameinsert내용-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#document-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1-dbcollection_nameinsert%EB%82%B4%EC%9A%A9-\" aria-label=\"document 생성 dbcollection_nameinsert내용  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Document 생성 (db.COLLECTION_NAME.insert(내용) )</h3>\n<p>Document는 <code class=\"language-text\">insert()</code> 메소드를 사용한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token operator\">></span> db.gugu.insert<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string\">'name'</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'고등어'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nWriteResult<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"nInserted\"</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> db.gugu.find<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"_id\"</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> ObjectId<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"5ed232c5dea93c027bea626f\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>, <span class=\"token string\">\"name\"</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"고등어\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"document-제거--dbcollection_nameremovecriteria-justone-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#document-%EC%A0%9C%EA%B1%B0--dbcollection_nameremovecriteria-justone-\" aria-label=\"document 제거  dbcollection_nameremovecriteria justone  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Document 제거 ( db.COLLECTION_NAME.remove(criteria, justOne) )</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">re